    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Fortunately, since developers are already on the web, the answer usually isn’t too hard to find.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And, once they’ve done this a few times, they’ll typically ",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "remember",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": " what they learned, ensuring they’ll never have to look it up next time.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s an apt metaphor. Because, after all, no one is perfect. And now, more than ever, no one has all the answers.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But knowing their’s a solution, a workaround, something that’s worked before—and having the willingness, the skill, and the eye to find it—that’s a quality worth investing in.",
